msgstr "在通过索引访问参数之前，请确保该方法具有足够的参数。否则，在计算缓存键时可能会抛出 `IndexOutOfBoundsException` 异常。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The following key generator will be instantiated using its default constructor:"
msgstr "以下密钥生成器将使用其默认构造函数进行实例化："

