msgstr "将方法名包含在缓存键中并不耗时，这与` `Method` `类中的其他方法不同。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Both kinds of key generators can be used in a similar way:"
msgstr "这两种密钥生成器的使用方法大致相同："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/cache.adoc
#, fuzzy
